'''Nullify Most Attacks''' is a [[Status Effect]] in {{XC3FR}}. It causes most attacks to miss the affected character. [[Alpha]] is able to gain this buff when using [[Monado Speed]].

{{clr}}

== Trivia ==
* The icon for this buff is similar to the icon for [[Shulk]]'s [[Battle Arts (XC1)|Talent Art]], Activate Monado, in {{XC}}.

